cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SOC, cs.LG

This paper deals with the analysis of language change in social media, specifically Twitter. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses statistical analysis and modeling techniques, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The paper also explores the relationship between language change and demographic/geographic factors, which could fall under cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
